{520}{}{To Bob from Jim.}
{521}{}{Bob, I hope this recording reaches you, because you and I won't be seeing each other again.
The Doc is merciless; by his words, I've got two or three days left before I head off to the other world.

I was going to make it to the meeting spot on time, but some grim-faced fellows caught up with me and started shaking me down.
You know me, I don't put up with that kind of garbage, I drew my piece right away and put a bullet in one of them.
A shootout broke out, I finished off two. But they got me too. Those cretins bolted with their tails between their legs, leaving me to die.
I patched up the wound as best I could and crawled to the Doc.

I left your share of the loot in a wooden box out in the Wasteland. Find the abandoned camp in the wasteland, not far from the meeting spot.
Landmarks - there are some arrows laid out of stones on the ground, and campfires around an idol.. In that camp, in one of the tents, you'll find what's yours by right.

Don't think ill of me, Bob. Tell my wife I tried...
Jim.}

