{540}{}{Letter of the Brotherhood of Steel paladins}
{541}{}{The Cossacks' Reply to Mehmed IV

The Zaporozhian Cossacks to the Turkish Sultan!

You - Turkish shaitan, brother and comrade of the cursed devil himself, and secretary to Lucifer in person! What kind of devil's knight are you, when you can't even kill a hedgehog with your bare arse? The devil shits, and your army devours it. You will never, you son of a bitch, have the sons of Christians under you; we are not afraid of your army, by land and by water we'll do battle with you, screw your mother.
You Babylonian cook, Macedonian wheelwright, Jerusalem brewer, Alexandrian goat-flayer, swineherd of Greater and Lesser Egypt, Podolian thief, Tatar quiver, hangman of Kamianets, jester of all the world and the underworld, a fool before our God, grandson of the Serpent himself and a hook on our prick. Pig's snout, mare's arse, butcher's dog, unbaptized brow, screw your mother!
That's how the Cossacks have answered you, you wretch! You are not fit to rule the mother of faithful Christians! We don't know the date, for we have no calendar; the moon's in the sky, the year's in the book, and the day's the same for us as for you, so kiss our arse for that!..

Signed: Otaman Ivan Sirko with the whole Zaporozhian Host}

